data.description: Introducing the epitome of modern living; a stunning 5-bedroom home with the ultimate convenience of main floor laundry.  This contemporary masterpiece is designed to meet the needs of the modern family, providing a seamless blend of comfort and functionality.  Main floor features spacious living area, open kitchen, pantry and 12x12 private patio.  Relax in the cozy living room or enjoy the seamless flow of indoor-outdoor living.  You will find a spacious master suite and three more bedrooms to provide plenty of space for your families or guests, or turn one into a home office.  There is an additional bedroom in the basement level with a full bathroom.  Don't miss your opportunity to own this exquisite newer home with main floor laundry. Schedule a showing today before it's gone!
